STATE
v.
Dennis Marshall CLEMMONS. No. 91A07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 3, 2007. Francis W. Crawley, Special Deputy Attorney General, Susan Doyle, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 20th day of April 2007 by Defendant to Withdraw as Counsel:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference this the 3rd day of May 2007."
